00:30.374 --> 00:33.258
We are so glad that you've chosen to worship with us here today.

00:33.278 --> 00:40.989
No matter how you're connecting or tuning in, maybe you're checking us out on TV, maybe you're online, or maybe you're listening to this at a later date.

00:41.069 --> 00:45.375
No matter how you're connecting here, we are glad that you've chosen to worship with us.

00:45.435 --> 00:46.597
And we want to thank you.

00:46.637 --> 00:53.426
